=== Version 3.0.7

* Update dependencies

=== Version 3.0.6

* Fix potential memory leak when device initialization fails
* Set limit to the size of read data to avoid potential buffer overflow
* Add 'log-level' command line flag to support enabling/disabling log levels: trace, debug, info, warn, error, fatal and panic
* Deprecate command line flag 'debug'

=== Version 3.0.5

* Increase maximum message size the connector can handle
* Fix compatibility with later Go versions 

